us d’appropriation de l’événement et des textes conciliaires par les religieuses et de revisiter une période riche d’espoirs et de turbulences.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aCouncils and synodszQuébec (Province)zMontréalxReception. 0aWomen in the Catholic ChurchzQuébec (Province)zMontréal. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311127253508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020z978311127473740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763749846423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763749846/original  a978-3-11-127253-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-127473-7  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles